OL,6,FA man who was given infected blood
OL,7,Fduring treatment for leukaemia says
OL,8,Fliving with the consequences of an
OL,9,Finfected blood transfusion is "like a
OL,10,Flife sentence".
OL,12,FStuart Hall, from Stainburn, near ,
OL,13,Fspent his 18th birthday in 1984 on a
OL,14,Fhospital ward fighting cancer. During
OL,15,Fhis treatment, he was given multiple
OL,16,Fblood transfusions.
