OL,6,F"I'd spent years going through
OL,7,Ftreatment for leukaemia and then I had
OL,8,Ften years of regular checkups for
OL,9,Fblood tests to make sure that the
OL,10,Fcancer hasn't come back," he explained.
OL,12,F"And just as I was getting to the tail
OL,13,Fend of all those checks and all that
OL,14,Fmonitoring, then a letter arrived to
OL,15,Ftell me I might be infected with a
OL,16,Fvirus.
