OL,6,F"It can lead to serious liver damage
OL,7,Fand liver cirrhosis and liver cancer
OL,8,Fand possibly death. And I lived with
OL,9,Fthat for 30 years. It takes a mental
OL,10,Ftoll. It's it's like a life sentence."
OL,12,FWhat is the infected blood inquiry?
OL,14,FDuring the 1970s and 1980s, more than
OL,15,F30,000 people in the UK were given
OL,16,Ftreatments infected with HIV and
OL,17,FHepatitis C.
