OL,6,FThe final report by the government's
OL,7,Finquiry was published today (Monday 20
OL,8,FMay 2024). It is one of the largest
OL,9,Fpublic inquiries in UK history.
OL,11,FWhat are the key findings from the
OL,12,Freport?
OL,14,FIn 2022, the inquiry's chairman, Sir
OL,15,FBrian Langstaff, recommended that
OL,16,Fcompensation of #100,000 should be
OL,17,Fpayed to those who received infected
OL,18,Fblood or to the partners of those who
OL,19,Fdied as a result of it.
