OL,6,FStuart was given a liver transplant in
OL,7,F2021 and now lives happily with his
OL,8,Fwife at home.
OL,10,FHe said when it comes to compensation,
OL,11,Fthe government is "kicking the can
OL,12,Fdown the road", adding: "People would
OL,13,Fsay to me: 'are you going to sue?' But
OL,14,Fwhy would I sue the hospital when they
OL,15,Fwere looking after me and treating me
OL,16,Ffor a life-threatening illness?
