OL,6,F"At that point, I was totally unaware
OL,7,Fof the knowledge that the government
OL,8,Fand the medical profession had that
OL,9,Fthere was potentially a high risk of
OL,10,Fblood donations having the virus
OL,11,Fwithin it.J"It makes me extremely
OL,12,Fangry. When you think that how much
OL,13,Fit's affected my life over the last
OL,14,Falmost 30 years - it's just
OL,15,Fridiculous. It's absolutely
OL,16,Fscandalous."
OL,18,FITV Border reporter Kieran Macfadzean
OL,19,Fspeaks to infected blood victim Stuart
OL,20,FHall about his hopes for compensation
