OL,6,F"I hope the government will issue a
OL,7,Fformal apology to everyone," he
OL,8,Fcontinued.
OL,10,F"I hope they will get on and finally
OL,11,Fdeal with the compensation. I think
OL,12,Fthey are dragging their heels.
OL,14,F"I think they were trying to kick the
OL,15,Fcan as far down the road as they could
OL,16,Fpossibly kick it because the bill for
OL,17,Fthis is potentially huge."
