OL,6,FA spokesperson for the UK Government
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was an appalling tragedy
OL,8,Fthat never should have happened. We
OL,9,Fare clear that justice needs to be
OL,10,Fdone, and swiftly.
OL,12,F"This includes establishing a new body
OL,13,Fto deliver an Infected Blood
OL,14,FCompensation Scheme, it will have all
OL,15,Fthe funding needed to deliver
OL,16,Fcompensation once they have identified
OL,17,Fthe victims and assessed claims.
OL,19,F"We will continue to listen carefully
OL,20,Fto the community as we address this
OL,21,Fdreadful scandal."
